{"tid":1212178,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 美國將推出《香港人權與民主法案》懲罰香港大陸高官（2）","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T09:29:40.000Z","uid":1251,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e36fdcbfe0832efbab464011f4320819a2840a2b","tid":1212178,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:35:55.000Z","msg":"《香港人權與民主法案》法案目的, 是對涉及鎮壓香港基本自由的香港或中國大陸的政府官員，設立懲罰機制，包括禁止涉事官員入境美國及凍結其在美國之資產.<br />\n<br />\nJim McGovern係美國國會和行政當局中國委員會（CECC）既主席.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1138824083985113088\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1138824083985113088&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMaQBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=6e5ffdcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1138824083985113088&h=d5d83370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1138824083985113088</a><br />\n<br />\nRep. Jim McGovern<br />\n&rlm;Verified account @RepMcGovern<br />\n<br />\n1/ I'm proud to stand with the people of #HongKong. Passage of the #ExtraditionLaw would put Hong Kong human rights advocates, business persons, journalists and American citizens at risk of rendition to mainland #China<br />\n<br />\n2/ I urge Chief Executive #CarrieLam &amp; #LegCo President #AndrewLeung to withdraw the current bill and explore alternatives that preserve #HongKong&rsquo;s autonomy and protect human rights and the rule of law.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3/ As the people of #HongKong continue peaceful demonstrations, the Police Commissioner and Secretary for Security should direct #HongKong police to refrain from using excessive force and intimidation and I urge them to protect the right to free expression.<br />\n<br />\n4/ Strong protections for human rights and rule of law are the foundation of Hong Kong&rsquo;s prosperity &amp; flourishing U.S.-Hong Kong relations. If the extradition law passes, Congress must look to revise the Hong Kong Policy Act of 1992 to reflect the erosion of autonomy.<br />\n<br />\n5/5 This week I will join @marcorubio &amp; @RepChrisSmith in introducing the &ldquo;HK Human Rights &amp; Democracy Act&rdquo; to reaffirm U.S. commitment to human rights &amp; the rule of law at a time when Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy is imperiled by Chinese gov't interference &amp; a revised #ExtraditionLaw.<br />\n7219<br />\n12"},{"pid":"65ca2686ceabc95e17e84a8ad1d4180b93b8f1c2","tid":1212178,"uid":1251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"眾連登巴打絲打準備好未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBackup所有相同片<br />\n到時用黎帶路用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />This way!"},{"pid":"8e81a052ed4cbf1a875281c530f7d0949a0bf24e","tid":1212178,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8183c4be60b6a5c01fe4f2b18f263388963428da","tid":1212178,"uid":7081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:54:22.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8075757dc8fb5c036b632a3b94b2253f2b3fa5bd","tid":1212178,"uid":135162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:57:23.000Z","msg":"要死都要拉埋班仆街落地獄"},{"pid":"0bcc210f5c0f86f9040c93ed19bcefc79f1e508a","tid":1212178,"uid":196327,"like":0,"disl